    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example is equipped with the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, delivering crisp gear selection through a short-throw linkage. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain optimal suspension geometry under load. Power is delivered to the tarmac via the factory M-Variable differential lock, ensuring predictable lateral grip and exit speeds. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and VANOS system inspection. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical integrity remains robust, offering a pure analog driving experience with a linear torque curve and exceptional throttle response.",
      "price": 34500.0,
