      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers a sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and is mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical maintenance items have been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The variable M differential lock provides excellent traction exit-corner, while the suspension maintains its factory-spec damping and bushing compliance. While the exterior displays minor patina expected of a driven enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain remains vigorous with a clean sweep to its 8,000 RPM redline. A driver-focused example for those who value mechanical purity and chassis feedback.",
